name: Resilient Nodes
description:
Every node in the network contributes to its strength.
A strong core and a cohesive community is key to getting back on our feet quickly when various external forces knock us down.

This piece is a donation to the relief efforts (Bangon) for the victims of typhoon Odette in the Philippines. 

Architecture-like elements randomly distributed in Blender Geometry Nodes
4320 x 4320 png
08 Jan 22

Artist: warrragwag (@jvlive_H)
